creator: Raddish.io
descriptionHtml:
Introducing the Raddish Wallet! Raddish Wallet is the *first* Android mobile wallet for the Radix DLT ecosystem!

Features of this wallet include:

- Wallet creation and imports
- Multi-wallet, multi-address support
- Ability to display, send, and receive XRD or any other tokens
- QR Code reader for receiving payments
- Ability to stake or unstake XRD to/from any validator

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: - Fixes to Ledger Nano S and X hardware wallet support

title: Raddish Wallet

descriptionHtml:
Introducing the RadBag Wallet! RadBag Wallet is the *first* Android mobile wallet for the Radix DLT ecosystem!

Features of this wallet include:

- Multi-wallet, multi-address support
- Ability to display, send, and receive XRD or any other tokens

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- Rebranded as RadBag Wallet! ... to prevent a name conflict with another Radix project that existed previously to this wallet
- Fiat prices! XRD and DogeCube token fiat prices are now displayed! (more tokens to be supported in the future)
- Ability to send a message/memo as part of a token transfer transaction!
- Ability to copy addresses from transaction history!
- Links to the official Radix Explorer from the transaction history!
